Building from scratch:

    ant clean jar

Running a single test:

    ant -Dtest=GrepConfigurationTest test


Runing a sigle test in debug mode:

    export ANT_OPTS="-Xdebug -Xnoagent -Djava.compiler=NONE -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_shmem,server=y,suspend=y,address=antjunit"
    ant -Dtest=GrepConfigurationTest test

